<h2>Directions</h2>
<p>Steep the Chai tea bags in the hot water for 3 to 5 minutes.</p>
<p>Warm milk in a pan, then whisk with a frother. Combine the milk and chai tea and add honey or sugar to taste. Sprinkle with cinnamon or nutmeg.</p>
